generate reviews datasets with businesses in city of Las Vegas, with businesses
havning at least 500 reviews and with users having at least 50 reviews, using
get_reviews_conditions method in preprocess.py file, and save it as csv file

generate train, test datasets using get_train_test_conditioned method in
models.py file, pass appropriate paths to save train, test methods by 
changing appropriate file variables

update file variables in load_train_test method of models.py file

run models.py file using "python3 models.py" command

You can change the number of topics for LDA by changing n_topics value in
run_lda method 
